comment._content: This is Alice, wife of Prince Alexander of Teck. She was born as Princess Alice of Albany and was a grand-daughter of Queen Victoria. Later she was styled Her Royal Highness Princess Alice, Countess of Athlone. en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Princess_Alice,_Countess_of_Athlone
